=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔需要迫佢任何野！投其所好！ <br />\n<br />\n想唔想tg傾下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我信得過我女朋友 <br />\n相信佢唔會咁做<br />\nbtw 謝巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年我都識左ex四年先一齊，都冇諗過佢會係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw我當然都希望自己只係個別例子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝你地快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1729c0905405995fd7ccb8ba62c1178aaa1bce6","tid":197171,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/093614_a180b6ea16fdd38bc4a7f5d5f71d88ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F093614_a180b6ea16fdd38bc4a7f5d5f71d88ab.jpg&h=47b1d277&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x96ihs1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx96ihs1.jpg&h=9e902d42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/093616_acdbde2a828b1ffee9d7460c7ce5762a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F093616_acdbde2a828b1ffee9d7460c7ce5762a.jpg&h=e0f2fcac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3X25s3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3X25s3.jpg&h=fd98dc4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/093651_8d3662cedfd4381e5c3d5677e8ef7754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F093651_8d3662cedfd4381e5c3d5677e8ef7754.jpg&h=dd3e610b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:同你女朋友一樣<br />\n但我比我男朋友話煩 唔想知 